    <h1>Notes API Instructions</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the Notes API. Here are the available endpoints:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>POST /users/signup</strong> - Sign up a new user</li>
        <li><strong>POST /users/signin</strong> - Sign in an existing user</li>
        <li><strong>GET /notes</strong> - Get all notes for the authenticated user</li>
        <li><strong>POST /notes</strong> - Create a new note</li>
        <li><strong>PUT /notes/:id</strong> - Update a note by ID</li>
        <li><strong>DELETE /notes/:id</strong> - Delete a note by ID</li>
    </ul>
